	<clause id="_packaging" inline-header="false" obligation="normative"><title>Packaging</title><p id="_0ee91d92-9f45-4ee0-ad1e-83dd76914bb1">The packaging shall not transmit any odour or flavour to the product and shall not contain substances which may damage the product or constitute a health risk.</p>
	<p id="_371f78a5-22ba-471c-ad42-eb8e4a3f1427">If bags are used, they shall comply with the requirements of <eref type="inline" bibitemid="ISO8351-1" citeas="ISO 8351-1:1994"><localityStack><locality type="clause"><referenceFrom>9</referenceFrom></locality></localityStack></eref>, or <eref type="inline" bibitemid="ISO8351-2" citeas="ISO 8351-2"/>, as appropriate.</p></clause>
