	<p id="_e8ac2a76-84c6-454a-8779-a2a572b793c0">consisting of a conical sample divider or multiple-slot sample divider with a distribution system, e.g. “Split-it-right” sample divider, such as that shown in <xref target="figureA-1"/>.</p>
	</clause>
