	<title>Principle</title>
	<p id="_ff430900-0c7b-4de8-a45b-783913766b6b">Waxy rice kernels have a reddish brown colour when stained in an iodine solution, while non-waxy rice kernels show a dark blue colour.</p>
	</clause>
